<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #2c003e, #3f000f);
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #ff4d4d;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px #000;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: rgba(255, 69, 69, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .music .playlist {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }

        iframe {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .workout ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .workout li {
            background: #cc0000;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .quotes blockquote {
            font-style: italic;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff4d4d;
            padding-left: 15px;
            color: #ffd6d6;
        }

        .rant h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ffa3a3;
        }

        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ff4d4d;
            background: #1a0000;
            color: white;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        button[type="submit"] {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #ff3333;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        button[type="submit"]:hover {
            background: #cc0000;
        }

        .container>div {
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.3);
            /* Light red line */
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>
    <h1>😤 You seem angry. Let’s channel that energy.</h1>
    <main class="body">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="music">
                <div class="playlist">Here is a playlist to lighten your mood</div>
                <!-- <iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/37i9dQZF1DX3YSRoSdA634"
                    width="100%" height="380" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""
                    allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"></iframe> -->
                    <iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/37i9dQZF1DX2pSTOxoPbx9?utm_source=generator" width="100%" height="380" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"></iframe>


            </div>
            <div class="workout">
                <h3>💪 Quick Stress-Buster Workout</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Jumping jacks 30sec</li>
                    <li>Pushups 3*10</li>
                    <li>Punch-in-the-air 30sec</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="quotes">
                <h3>🧠 Quote to Reflect</h3>
                <blockquote>"Holding onto anger is like drinking poison and expecting the other person to die."
                </blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="rant">
                <h3>📝 Rant Box</h3>
                <form action="/submit-rant" method="post">
                    <textarea name="rant" rows="4" placeholder="Let it out...(This will be a secret)"></textarea>
                    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>

</html>